DISCLAIMER FOR EDUCATIONAL USE:
This software is designed for educational and research purposes. It demonstrates
federated learning concepts and should not be used in production healthcare
environments without proper validation, security audits, and compliance reviews.
The privacy mechanisms implemented are for demonstration purposes and may require
additional safeguards for real-world healthcare applications.

HEALTHCARE DATA NOTICE:
This project uses synthetic and publicly available datasets for demonstration.
Any real healthcare data should be handled according to applicable regulations
such as HIPAA, GDPR, and other privacy laws. Users are responsible for ensuring
compliance with all relevant data protection regulations in their jurisdiction.
